{"tid":1973850,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台再零確診「鼓舞人心」","createTime":"2020-04-15T12:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T14:18:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"75d196a37b2566d31451c62a80edd61c8ae4e2e1","tid":1973850,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200415/GJC53EW66JZP3QZZSPEVPF2DZA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200415%2FGJC53EW66JZP3QZZSPEVPF2DZA%2F&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQGWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=d198805f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200415%2FGJC53EW66JZP3QZZSPEVPF2DZA%2F&h=34a22934\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200415/GJC53EW66JZP3QZZSPEVPF2DZA/</a><br />\n<br />\n台再零確診「鼓舞人心」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200415/large/1586882581_5e04.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200415%2Flarge%2F1586882581_5e04.gif&h=ef7cb7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣昨再公佈沒有單日新增確診個案，總統蔡英文也在fb說「這就是最能鼓舞人心的好消息」。<br />\n<br />\n事隔個多月，台灣昨再公佈沒有單日新增確診個案，總統蔡英文也在fb說「這就是最能鼓舞人心的好消息」。不過，也非所有台灣人都齊心抗疫，早前四名從美國返台的一個家庭，家居檢疫期間，居然乘的士去醫院檢查，其中一人隨後被驗出確診武肺，當地衞生部門向他們開罰合共170萬元新台幣（下同，約43.9萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n台灣中央流行疫情指揮中心表示，昨日當地沒有新增的確診病例，維持393宗個案，上次台灣出現零新增確診是上月7日至9日。蔡英文也在fb講到民間於《紐約時報》登廣告時提及，「台灣能被國際社會肯定，也是因為全民同心協力落實防疫。今天的零確診，就是最能鼓舞人心的好消息。」另外，台北知名的圓山飯店也首次啟用牌樓燈光，打出「ZERO」慶祝台灣零確診防疫成績，並感謝醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一家違令外出罰44萬<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：拒設失業援助金 籲申請綜援<br />\n<br />\n不過，在台灣也並非所有人都有如蔡英文所說同心抗疫。基隆四名從美國返台的家庭成員，上月21日檢疫期間，因其中一人體溫升高，自行帶同媳婦與兩名孫子搭的士前往醫院，當時衞生局人員已力勸她，未有檢測結果不能外出，但婦人仍堅持外出，最後更驗出她和同住的丈夫確診武漢肺炎，其餘同住的人和當日運載婦人前往醫院的的士司機檢測則呈陰性，基隆市衞生局對當日有份出門的婦人和媳婦分別罰款100萬元（約25.8萬港元）和70萬元（約18.1萬港元），至於兩名孫子則未成年，可依法不罰。外界擔心該婦人會成為台灣的防疫缺口，中央流行疫情指揮中心發言人莊人祥表示，該婦人搭載期間的士司機有戴口罩，並沒有所謂的缺口。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"6ac4ef5ffaa5673ac3b9b01b2affd7796747e5b6","tid":1973850,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:39:23.000Z","msg":"恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e10002951c8116b3cf51c52e977ab8ffc8c015","tid":1973850,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"Monkey queen: eeeeerrrrrrrrrrrrrrr"},{"pid":"0e3a2ad4b658b9515ca55a66166258816a0f5193","tid":1973850,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:46:20.000Z","msg":"Good show"},{"pid":"217e320db893623c01b22ff1949fa94451d19647","tid":1973850,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:46:25.000Z","msg":"good show<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859e029c549f37a2d93e48f2cc8bd70a7d81d29f","tid":1973850,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e3a2ad4b658b9515ca55a66166258816a0f5193","tid":1973850,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:46:20.000Z","msg":"Good show"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"快過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33b7dcc56ca06150c9b77262c125ae576aab3b2","tid":1973850,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T12:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126529e58ff255570e1338c2ff8150e0ef13f66f","tid":1973850,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1